WEBVTT

00:00:58.260 --> 00:01:01.940
She laughs and says,
"Oh, precious, stand up.

00:01:01.964 --> 00:01:04.588
Say D-O-G."

00:01:04.612 --> 00:01:07.020
And I respond,
[In a Staten Island accent] "Dog?"

00:01:07.044 --> 00:01:10.847
The class broke out in laughter
along with the teacher.

00:01:11.282 --> 00:01:12.804
And so it went,

00:01:12.828 --> 00:01:16.063
because she had many more words
to humiliate me with.

00:01:17.230 --> 00:01:19.413
I went home sobbing,

00:01:19.437 --> 00:01:20.729
distraught

00:01:20.753 --> 00:01:23.077
and begging to be sent back to New York

00:01:23.101 --> 00:01:25.204
or to some nunnery.

00:01:25.228 --> 00:01:28.541
I did not want to go back
to that school again. No way.

00:01:29.168 --> 00:01:30.855
My parents listened